    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to be listing this absolute beauty. It\u2019s in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! The paint is flawless, the interior is spotless, and it drives like a total dream. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. You\u2019ve really gotta see this one in person to believe how clean it is. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
