    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You\u2019ve got to see this beauty in person\u2014it is honestly in absolutely incredible shape! It\u2019s been pampered its whole life, kept in a climate-controlled garage, and looks just as stunning as the day it rolled off the lot. Not a single scratch or blemish to be found. It drives like an absolute dream, and I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44500.0,
