    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering. Under the hood, the S54B32 inline-six remains in pristine mechanical health, featuring six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing that pulls flawlessly to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag six-speed manual transmission offers tight, precise throws, delivering power to the rear wheels via the original variable M differential lock. The chassis is structurally immaculate, with a documented subframe reinforcement and fresh bushings throughout to maintain factory kinematic geometry. Every body panel retains its original factory finish with consistent micrometer readings and zero oxidation. This is a collector-grade specimen with a fully sorted cooling system and preventative rod bearing replacement already completed, ensuring turn-key performance for the purist driver.",
